title: How does the proportion of people with diabetes receiving the recommended care processes differ by age?
analysis_commentary: Analysis by age groups reveals that rates of completion for all eight care processes is much lower for the youngest group (under 40), and especially for people with Type 1 diabetes.
data_source: National Diabetes Audit, HQIP, IC, Diabetes UK
